Class TraceUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.trace.TraceUtil

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
public final class TraceUtil
extends Object
    This wrapper class provides functions for accessing htrace 4+ functionality in a simplified way.
